cp|red|at|^*bOliverC:^*n|cp||at|  The Asking Bid we're going to look at tonight is Sigma, a fairly new addition to our weaponry.

Sigma occurs in one place only, which is IMMEDIATELY over a POSITIVE response to Alpha (NOT after a 1 or 2 step response).
|lg|i|n#|5|at|^^
