^bIf the newly agreed trump suit is the next bid up or the bid over that (commonly after a 3 or 4-step response)
^cthen ^*b Sigma ^*n is
^*bthe of bid the agreed trump suit ^*n  (and the bid is below game level)    ^d@2
1@c  -  1@h  -  1@s(Alpha)   -   2@h(4+ ctls & support)    ^o-   2@s    is Sigma in @s's. 
1@c  -  2@d  -  3@c(Alpha)   -   3@s(0-3 ctrls & support)  ^o-   4@c    is Sigma in @c's.
|n#|h|at|^bIf the agreed trump suit is not in the next 2 bids above the Alpha response (commonly after a 5+ step response)
^cthen ^*b Sigma ^*n is
^b^*bthe next bid up ^*n (and Relay Beta, if required, is "bumped") 
1@c  -  1@h  -  1@s(Alpha)  -  2@s(4 ctrls & @sHxxx)  ^o-  2NT is Sigma in @s's
1@c  -  2@d  -  3@c(Alpha)  -  4@d(5 ctrls & @cHxxx)  ^o-  4@h is Sigma in @c's|
