cp|red|at|^*bOliverC:^*n|cp||at|  If Sigma is used and the response shows 2 or more top honours then a relay over the Response is Beta.

If Responder showed No Top Honours or only 1 then the Relay is a repeat Sigma (see later) and the next bid after that is Beta.

Let me stress, a Repeat Sigma is ONLY available if Responder shows No Top Honours or only 1 top honour.

If responder shows 1 or no top honours in response to Sigma, then a Repeat sigma is permitted to ask if Responder has the Jack of the trump suit.

Now 1 step denies and 2 steps promises.

If a Repeat Sigma is used, then a relay over the response is Relay Beta if required, otherwise Epsilon.|
