cp|red|at|^*bOliverC:^*n|cp||at|  Repeat Sigma is available when Responder shows     NO top honours     ^*bor^*n    only 1 top honour.  

If Opener themselves has only 1 top honour, then the presence or absence of the Jack adds considerably to the chances of you losing a trump trick in addition to any other controls you might be missing.

Sigma is used quite rarely,  as it can easily use up space that is normally better used for Epsilons.

